<h3 id="marketplace-metadata">Other meta data</h3>
<div class="api-docs-basics">
    <p>
        The <b>meta</b> folder also contains the <b>images</b> folder with files that are needed to display your plugin as an item in plentyMarketplace, such as preview images, the author icon and the plugin icon.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="api-docs-basics">
    <table class="table table-striped table-responsive table-bordered table-hover">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>File</th>
                <th>Description</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>

        <tbody>
            <tr>
                <td>Author icon</td>
                <td>The author icon. Valid file formats are PNG and JPEG. The author icon must be specified in the <code>plugin.json</code>. The icon can have the following image sizes:
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <b>icon_author_xs</b>: 32x32 px
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <b>icon_author_sm</b>: 256x256 px
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <b>icon_author_md</b>: 512x512 px
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Plugin icon</td>
                <td>The plugin icon. Valid file formats are PNG and JPEG. The plugin icon must be specified in the <code>plugin.json</code>. The icon can have the following image sizes:
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <b>icon_plugin_xs</b>: 32x32 px
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <b>icon_plugin_sm</b>: 256x256 px
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <b>icon_plugin_md</b>: 512x512 px
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Preview images</td>
                <td>The preview images of the plugin to be displayed in plentyMarketplace. Valid file formats are PNG and JPEG. The maximum file size for preview images is 1 MB. Upload up to 7 preview images, e.g. <code>preview_0.jpeg</code>, <code>preview_1.jpeg</code> etc.</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>

